## Proposed QIP upgrades
1. Fix indexing bug
2. Initialize fees (100m Qubic for ICO Setup)
3. Adjust SC Re-distributions (5% Development Fund / 5% SC holders)
4. Create additional Options:
    - Vesting Periods (lock qubic revenue & remaining tokens for custom time periods. example: lock revenue & remaining tokens for 3 months following ICO, releasing only 5% monthly until 90 day period is complete) 
    - note: each release must be wallet approved. any amount left unapproved for 90 days goes to LP.
    - Optional Benchmark based fund disbursements(example: Once ICO concludes, Release (X) qubic to begin project. Once user-defined Milestones are met then Release (X) qubic to progress to next phase, etc.)
5. Burn Mechanism: burn (X)% of Token supply instead of returning to wallet.

